STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Rico PARKS a/k/a James R. Parks, Jameel Parks, Parks James, Jameel Partlow, James R. Partow, Riccio J. Park, Eric R. Parks, Eric Park, Reo Parks, Reko Parks, Reco Parks Jr., Reco J. Parks, Rico J. Parks, Parks R. James, Reco Parks, Defendant-Petitioner. C-582 September Term 2017
079959 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 2, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003753-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
